.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH d2b 1 1970-01-01 "d2b 0.0.0-bootstrap" "d2b CLI"
.SH NAME
d2b \- d2b — opinionated NixOS desktop microVM CLI.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBd2b\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
d2b — daemon\-native CLI for d2b microVMs.
.PP
Mutating verbs dispatch through d2bd; privileged host mutations additionally use d2b\-priv\-broker. Read\-only verbs (list, status, audit, host check) prefer d2bd\*(Aqs public socket and fall back to static/local sources where documented. See `d2b <COMMAND> \-\-help` for per\-verb usage.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
d2b\-list(1)
List declared VMs with daemon runtime state when d2bd is reachable
.TP
d2b\-status(1)
Show per\-VM runtime status plus bridge health
.TP
d2b\-launch(1)
Launch a trusted configured workload item through its runtime provider
.TP
d2b\-usb(1)
USB attach / detach / probe
.TP
d2b\-console(1)
Foreground serial console bridge for headless VMs
.TP
d2b\-audio(1)
Per\-VM audio status and grant controls
.TP
d2b\-audit(1)
Tail the broker audit log
.TP
d2b\-host(1)
Host\-side preflight, install, doctor, and reconcile verbs
.TP
d2b\-auth(1)
Authorisation introspection
.TP
d2b\-realm(1)
Low\-level realm gateway helpers
.TP
d2b\-shell(1)
Attach to or manage persistent named guest shells
.TP
d2b\-op(1)
Inspect current constellation operation and trace state
.TP
d2b\-vm(1)
Per\-VM lifecycle verbs (start / stop / restart / list / status) plus the admin\-only guest\-control sub\-verb `exec`, which runs commands or an interactive session inside a VM over the authenticated guest\-control transport (no SSH)
.TP
d2b\-up(1)
Alias for `vm start <vm>`
.TP
d2b\-down(1)
Alias for `vm stop <vm>`
.TP
d2b\-restart(1)
Alias for `vm restart <vm>`
.TP
d2b\-build(1)
Non\-destructive eval + build of the per\-VM toplevel
.TP
d2b\-generations(1)
List current / booted / numbered generations for a VM
.TP
d2b\-switch(1)
Atomically activate a new per\-VM closure
.TP
d2b\-boot(1)
Stage a per\-VM closure for the next boot only
.TP
d2b\-test(1)
Activate a per\-VM closure with rollback on reboot
.TP
d2b\-rollback(1)
Roll a VM back to its previous generation
.TP
d2b\-gc(1)
Garbage\-collect the per\-VM /nix/store hardlink farm
.TP
d2b\-store(1)
Store\-view maintenance and verification
.TP
d2b\-keys(1)
Managed\-key lifecycle (list / show / rotate)
.TP
d2b\-trust(1)
Trust a VM\*(Aqs host key on first use (TOFU)
.TP
d2b\-rotate\-known\-host(1)
Rotate the consumer\*(Aqs recorded known\-host entry for a VM
.TP
d2b\-migrate(1)
Analyse the host config and emit a migration plan
.TP
d2b\-config(1)
Sync / review / approve a VM\*(Aqs guest\-editable config (`guestConfigFile`): pull the operator\*(Aqs in\-VM edits to a host\-side staging file, diff them, and approve them
.TP
d2b\-clipboard(1)
Clipboard authority operations (picker\-driven paste replay via d2b\-clipd)
.TP
d2b\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
.SH VERSION
v0.0.0\-bootstrap
